{"serial": "41008", "department_serial": 40, "code": "BA2016", "class": "B", "name": {"en": "Cost Accounting", "ch": "成本會計"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Huang, Cheng-Tsu"], "ch": ["黃承祖"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 1, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "I1", "room": "111"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 70, "department": {"ch": "企業管理學系", "en": "Department of Business Administration"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "全部使用", "en": "All"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 65, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "成本會計提供財務會計與管理會計所需之攸關資訊，管理者可依據成本會計所取得之資訊，向外部人出具財務報表，亦可藉此資訊對組織進行規劃、制定策略並進行控制與檢討，涉及企業的預算編制、成本控制、產品訂價、利潤計算、績效評估與薪酬制度等。本課程介紹傳統成本會計的成本計算、帳務處理、成本分析，及成本會計現行管理新課題，亦涵蓋部份管理會計範圍。", "en": "“COSTS: CONCEPTS AND OBJECTIVES\nCOST ACCUMULATION\nPLANNING AND CONTROL OF COSTS\nBUDGETING AND STANDARD COSTS\nANALYSIS OF COSTS AND PROFIT“"}, "outline": {"ch": "“Ch 1 Management, the Controller, and Cost Accounting\nCh 2 Cost Concepts and the Cost Accounting Information System\nCh 3 Cost Behavior Analysis\nCh 4 Cost Systems and Cost Accumulation\nCh 5 Job Order Costing\nCh 6 Process Costing\nCh 7 The Cost of Quality and Accounting for Production Losses\nCh 8 Costing By-Products and Joint Products\nCh 9 Materials: Controlling, Costing, and Planning\nCh10 Labor: Controlling and Accounting for Costs\nCh11 Factory Overhead: Departmentalization, Planned, Actual, and Applied\nCh12 Responsibility Accounting and Reporting\nCh13 Activity Accounting: Activity-Based Costing and Activity-Based Management\nCh14 Budgeting: Profits, Sales, Costs, and Expenses\nCh16 Standard Costing: Setting Standards and Analyzing Variances\nCh18 Direct Costing, Cost-Volume-Profit Analysis\nCh19 Differential Cost Analysis\nCh23 Profit Performance Measurements and Intracompany Transfer Pricing“", "en": "“Ch 1 Management, the Controller, and Cost A